Pennsylvania, and Iowa.

22:15.333 --> 22:20.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Campaign events give him greater
flexibility, like being able
to sell Make America Great

22:21.066 --> 22:23.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Again merchandise.

22:23.533 --> 22:25.066 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL STEEL, Republican
Strategist: This is
an opportunity for the
president to spread

22:25.066 --> 22:29.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
