active and energized supporters.

22:29.066 --> 22:34.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
It's also an opportunity
to raise money, to
sell merchandise.

22:36.000 --> 22:38.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
