22:49.133 --> 22:53.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
DONALD TRUMP: We are
going to start taking
care of our country.

22:53.566 --> 22:58.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN YANG: And they seem to
boost Mr. Trump's mood, getting
him out of Washington and in

22:59.633 --> 23:02.200 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
