his assets into a trust, of
which he's the sole beneficiary.

23:58.833 --> 24:02.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Ethics lawyer Kenneth Gross
says he's never seen a candidate
pay so much money to his

24:03.333 --> 24:05.433 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
own businesses.

24:05.433 --> 24:07.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
KENNETH GROSS, Ethics
Law Expert: What we saw
during the campaign is
the campaign committee

24:07.833 --> 24:12.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
paying Trump facilities,
whether it's the Trump Hotel
or Mar-a-Lago, or renting space

24:15.033 --> 24:20.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
