tick acts as a concentrating
vessel to allow you to

42:29.433 --> 42:31.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
better sample
what's in the host.

42:31.500 --> 42:35.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: After removing
these ticks, Dr. Hu will grind
them up and test them for

42:35.900 --> 42:37.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
