Lyme, Connecticut, and what came
to be known as Lyme disease.

43:25.466 --> 43:27.466 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

43:27.466 --> 43:29.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ALLEN STEERE, Massachusetts
General Hospital: My career
has largely been focused on the

43:29.466 --> 43:34.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
