disease by vaccination.

43:47.233 --> 43:52.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: The Lyme
disease vaccine which he helped
develop is a sore subject.

43:54.400 --> 43:58.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Sold under the brand
name LYMErix by
SmithKline Beecham, now
GlaxoSmithKline, it was first

43:58.966 --> 44:01.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
