44:29.933 --> 44:34.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Lyme disease is the only
infection that I know
of for which there is
an effective vaccine,

44:36.266 --> 44:38.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
