for the Prevention of
Cruelty to Animals.

44:54.300 --> 44:58.400 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Her owner is veterinarian
Susan O'Bell.

44:58.400 --> 45:02.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SUSAN O'BELL, Veterinarian: I
