people and their pets alike.

45:18.333 --> 45:22.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It sure seems like something
we should be working on to
prevent, one way or another.

45:22.533 --> 45:27.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: And, in fact,
the French biotech firm Valneva
is in the first phase of U.S.

45:29.533 --> 45:32.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Food and Drug Administration
testing on a new vaccine
