45:35.033 --> 45:39.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
In the 15 years since
the vaccine was pulled
off the market, Lyme
has exploded into an

45:40.733 --> 45:45.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
