takes on war crimes.

46:41.033 --> 46:44.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Jeffrey Brown has our
latest addition to the
"NewsHour" Bookshelf.

46:44.166 --> 46:49.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: In 2004,
400 people were rounded
up from their homes in
a village in Bosnia,

46:50.333 --> 46:52.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
